Sorry folks E-systems is giving me my cue to exit. (Messages like 
this page has expired) so either I have to close and go back to it or 
I have to sign off. I got things to do so try not to beat on my 
characters to much, I'll be back tomorrow morning to check our 
progress. Logo, try to keep Shadow Wing alive until I get back, (I 
got plans for her either way this turns out) Email ya some ideas 
later.

And check on KitKat and Phobia, I don't trust that spider (Pretty bad 
since he's me.

Until we meet again my friends I say farewell.
